# ==============================================================================
# File: hosts
# Description: 集群内网 IP 与主机名映射配置模板
# Usage: 
#   1. 必须删除或注释掉默认的 `127.0.0.1 localhost` 或 `127.0.1.1 <hostname>`
#      (否则会导致 ZK 监听回环地址、HDFS 节点注册失败等严重问题)
#   2. 替换下方的 <MASTER_IP>、<MASTER_HOSTNAME> 等占位符为你规划的实际网络参数
#   3. 分发并覆盖所有节点 (Master 和所有 Workers) 的 /etc/hosts 文件
# ==============================================================================

# --- 大数据集群内网映射配置开始 ---
<MASTER_IP>    <MASTER_HOSTNAME>
<WORKER1_IP>   <WORKER1_HOSTNAME>
<WORKER2_IP>   <WORKER2_HOSTNAME>
# --- 大数据集群内网映射配置结束 ---

# The following lines are desirable for IPv6 capable hosts
::1     ip6-localhost ip6-loopback
fe00::0 ip6-localnet
ff00::0 ip6-mcastprefix
ff02::1 ip6-allnodes
ff02::2 ip6-allrouters